review.reviewBody: Delicious and Fresh pastry. Babka is the best one I have ever had.

Palmier Was indeed delicious as usualüòãThis is my first review for them. Because just recently found place. So after several weeks of ordering their tasty food & quite regularly as well. So far sooo good. Definitely recommend this place. Reasonably priced too. Which is not common nowadaysüëç
This is my 2nd time trying this place. Finally, found a place that have actual Palmiers Delicious! üòã

I honestly wasn't expecting that much from this place, but it totally blew me away! So fresh, the flavours were fantastic, and best of all, they weren't too sweet! I will definitely be ordering from them again.
I did got the Fig & Walnut Rye Sourdough.
